extends layout

block content
	div
		div.page-header
			h1 Creating a Quiz
		div.container-fluid
			div.row
				h3 Question Numbers
				div.well 
					| Question numbers are automatically updated whenever you add or remove a new question!
			div.row
				h3 Choices
				div.well 
					| When adding choices for a question, they must be comma delimited (separated by commas). 
					| This is allows what you type to be broken up into mutliple choices and it's important for matching up the answer to the correct choice.
			div.row
				h3 Answer
				div.well 
					| When setting the answer for a question, input the choice number with the first choice being 0, second choice being 1, etc.